{"article_id":"iRxAPJzr2WWKtoiZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Tensions are again escalating between the U.S. and North Korea .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"On Friday , North Korea tested an intercontinental ballistic missile","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that experts say","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"may be capable of reaching the West Coast of the United States .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"North Korea says","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"the test was a warning to the United States","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to stop imposing sanctions against North Korea .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"KRT news reader :","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" The reason","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"why we conducted the maximum-range simulation of an intercontinental ballistic missile test launch","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"was to send a stern warning to the U.S. ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"which has applied sanctions against North Korea at this time ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"losing their minds .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"If the U.S. fails to come to its senses","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and continues to resort to military adventure and 'tough sanctions ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"' North Korea will respond with its resolute act of justice ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"as already declared . \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"In response to North Korea ' s test , the U.S. flew two B-1 bombers over the Korean Peninsula","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"and again tested its Alaska-based THAAD missile defense system .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"The U.S. has deployed a similar THAAD missile defense system to South Korea ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"despite objections from local residents .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"President Trump also took to Twitter","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"to complain","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that China was not doing enough","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"to counter North Korea ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"tweeting ,","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"\" I am very disappointed in China .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Our foolish past leaders have allowed them to make hundreds of billions of dollars a year in trade ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"yet they do NOTHING for us with North Korea ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"just talk .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"We will no longer allow this to continue .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"China could easily solve this problem ! \"","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Tensions have been rising between the U.S. and North Korea","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"since President Trump took office ,","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"exacerbated by Trump ' s erratic method","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"of conducting foreign policy on social media ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"without first consulting the Pentagon .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Last week ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"when Trump took to Twitter","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"to announce","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that he would be banning transgender people from serving in the U.S. military in three separate tweets ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"many military officials first thought","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"he was declaring war on North Korea .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"The first tweet read only","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"\" After consultation with my Generals and military experts ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"please be advised","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that the United States Government will not accept or allow ...... \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"The second tweet ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"ending the speculation ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"didn ' t come for another nine minutes .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":0,"right":98,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":80,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":69,"right":79,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":65,"right":68,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":52,